title: resnet34 output feature (32, 512, 1, 2) in pytcharm
body_html: Yesterday, I update pytorch to 0.4.0(python3). I uses pretrained resnet34 model. And I run in pycharm, it's feature shape in (32, 512, 1, 2). While in the "Python Console" (in pycharm), it's feature shape in (32, 512, 1, 1). And it's feature also shape right (32, 512, 1, 1) in Terminal. What's wrong with it?
